About
---------------
This is a easy, scalable, fast and secure PHP MVC framework for creating CRUD web applications.
The sole purpose for it, is to make web developers less aggressive aginst their keyboards.
Write less code for more money... or for some of you anyway ;-p

Install
---------------
1. Extract all files into your favourite development folder.
For example: /var/www/myFavouriteDevelopmentFolder, where I guess that you guessed that 
"myFavouriteDevelopmentFolder" is nothing more than a example name of the folder you choosed.

2. Run http://localhost/myFavouriteDevelopmentFolder/install.php
This gives you the option to enter MySQL credentials. The file is self-destructive by the way.

3. You should set up a reasonable .htaccess file like this;
<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
  SetEnv HTTP_MOD_REWRITE On
  RewriteEngine On
  RewriteBase /myFavouriteDevelopmentFolder

  RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} ^(.*)$
  RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
  RewriteRule .* index.php?url=%1&%{QUERY_STRING} [L]
</IfModule>

4. Start coding and enjoy!